Medical Biometric Equipment for New Employee Onboarding – MedLife

SYSTEM ANALYSIS & DESIGN (SAD)


1️⃣ PROJECT OVERVIEW
To securely onboard new employees at MedLife company, a Biometric Medical Equipment System has been designed.
This system captures employees’ biometric data (fingerprint / face – simulated), stores it securely, and uses it for future verification purposes.


